# ===== BERT-OPTIMIZED TURKISH ADDRESS PREPROCESSING =====
import re
from unidecode import unidecode

def bert_optimized_address_preprocessing(text):
    """
    BERT modeli iin optimize edilmi Trke adres preprocessing fonksiyonu.
    Tm preprocessing admlarn birletirir ve BERT'in en iyi performans iin tasarlanmtr.
    """
    if not isinstance(text, str) or not text.strip():
        return ""
    
    # Orijinal metni koru (baz analizler iin)
    original_text = text
    
    # --- PHASE 1: INITIAL CLEANING ---
    # Kk harfe evir
    text = text.lower().strip()
    
    # oklu boluklar ve tab/newline karakterlerini temizle
    text = re.sub(r'\s+', ' ', text)
    
    # --- PHASE 2: TURKISH CHARACTER NORMALIZATION ---
    # Trke karakterleri kontroll ekilde normalize et (BERT trke modeli iin optimize)
    turkish_normalization = {
        '': 'c', '': 'g', '': 'i', '': 'o', '': 's', '': 'u',
        '': 'a', '': 'i', '': 'u', '': 'o'
    }
    for tr_char, en_char in turkish_normalization.items():
        text = text.replace(tr_char, en_char)
    
    # --- PHASE 3: NUMBER & ALPHANUMERIC STANDARDIZATION ---
    # Say ve alfanmerik kodlar standardize et (BERT tokenization iin)
    
    # Alfanmerik kodlar ayr: 24/A  24 A, 12/B  12 B
    text = re.sub(r'\b(\d+)\s*[/\-\\]\s*([a-zA-Z]\d*)\b', r'\1 \2', text)
    
    # Say kombinasyonlarn ayr: 24/5  24 5, 3/12  3 12  
    text = re.sub(r'\b(\d+)\s*[/\-\\]\s*(\d+)\b', r'\1 \2', text)
    
    # Noktal saylar ayr: 24.5  24 5 (BERT iin)
    text = re.sub(r'\b(\d+)[.,](\d+)\b', r'\1 \2', text)
    
    # --- PHASE 4: COMPREHENSIVE ABBREVIATION EXPANSION ---
    # Trkiye'de yaygn kullanlan adres ksaltmalar
    abbreviations = {
        # Temel adres bileenleri
        r'\bmah\.?\b': 'mahallesi',
        r'\bmahalle\b': 'mahallesi',
        r'\bmhl\.?\b': 'mahallesi',
        
        r'\bsok\.?\b': 'sokak',
        r'\bsk\.?\b': 'sokak',
        r'\bsokagi\b': 'sokak',
        
        r'\bcad\.?\b': 'caddesi',
        r'\bcd\.?\b': 'caddesi',
        r'\bcaddesi\b': 'caddesi',
        
        r'\bblv\.?\b': 'bulvari',
        r'\bbulvar\b': 'bulvari',
        r'\bblvr\.?\b': 'bulvari',
        
        r'\bno\.?\b': 'numara',
        r'\bnumara\b': 'numara',
        r'\bnum\.?\b': 'numara',
        
        # Yap bileenleri
        r'\bapt\.?\b': 'apartmani',
        r'\bapartman\b': 'apartmani',
        r'\bapart\.?\b': 'apartmani',
        
        r'\bd\.?\b': 'daire',
        r'\bdaire\b': 'daire',
        r'\bdr\.?\b': 'daire',
        
        r'\bk\.?\b': 'kat',
        r'\bkat\b': 'kat',
        r'\bkati\b': 'kat',
        
        r'\bblok\b': 'blok',
        r'\bbl\.?\b': 'blok',
        
        # Site ve kompleks
        r'\bsit\.?\b': 'sitesi',
        r'\bsite\b': 'sitesi',
        r'\bkonut\.?\b': 'konutlari',
        r'\bkompleks\b': 'kompleksi',
        r'\brezidans\b': 'rezidansi',
        
        # Dier yaygn ksaltmalar
        r'\bpk\.?\b': 'park',
        r'\bpark\b': 'park',
        r'\bmez\.?\b': 'mezarligi',
        r'\bmeydan\b': 'meydani',
        r'\bmeyd\.?\b': 'meydani',
        r'\bk\.?\b': 'cikmaz',
        r'\bkmaz\b': 'cikmaz'
    }
    
    for abbr_pattern, full_form in abbreviations.items():
        text = re.sub(abbr_pattern, full_form, text, flags=re.IGNORECASE)
    
    # --- PHASE 5: GEOGRAPHIC STANDARDIZATION ---
    # Yn ve konum belirteleri
    directional_terms = {
        r'\bkuzey\b': 'kuzey',
        r'\bguney\b': 'guney',
        r'\bdogu\b': 'dogu',
        r'\bbati\b': 'bati',
        r'\bi\b': 'ic',
        r'\bii\b': 'ic',
        r'\bd\b': 'dis',
        r'\bd\b': 'dis',
        r'\balt\b': 'alt',
        r'\bst\b': 'ust',
        r'\bn\b': 'on',
        r'\barka\b': 'arka',
        r'\bsag\b': 'sag',
        r'\bsol\b': 'sol'
    }
    
    for direction_pattern, standardized in directional_terms.items():
        text = re.sub(direction_pattern, standardized, text, flags=re.IGNORECASE)
    
    # --- PHASE 6: CITY/DISTRICT NORMALIZATION ---
    # Byk ehir ve ile isimleri standardizasyonu
    major_locations = {
        r'\bist\.?\b': 'istanbul',
        r'\bistanbul\b': 'istanbul',
        r'\bank\.?\b': 'ankara',
        r'\bankara\b': 'ankara',
        r'\bizm\.?\b': 'izmir',
        r'\bizmir\b': 'izmir',
        r'\bbeyoglu\b': 'beyoglu',
        r'\bkadikoy\b': 'kadikoy',
        r'\bbesiktas\b': 'besiktas',
        r'\buskudar\b': 'uskudar',
        r'\bsisli\b': 'sisli',
        r'\bfatih\b': 'fatih',
        r'\besenler\b': 'esenler',
        r'\bbahcelievler\b': 'bahcelievler'
    }
    
    for location_pattern, standardized in major_locations.items():
        text = re.sub(location_pattern, standardized, text, flags=re.IGNORECASE)
    
    # --- PHASE 7: NOISE REMOVAL ---
    # Gereksiz kelime ve ifadeleri kaldr
    noise_patterns = [
        r'\bmevki\b', r'\bmevkii\b', r'\byakini\b', r'\bcivar\b',
        r'\bkarsisi\b', r'\bkarsisinda\b', r'\byani\b', r'\byaninda\b',
        r'\bonu\b', r'\bonunde\b', r'\barkasi\b', r'\barkasinda\b',
        r'\biinde\b', r'\bierisinde\b', r'\buzerinde\b', r'\baltinda\b'
    ]
    
    for noise_pattern in noise_patterns:
        text = re.sub(noise_pattern, '', text, flags=re.IGNORECASE)
    
    # --- PHASE 8: FEATURE EXTRACTION & TAGGING ---
    features = []
    
    # Posta kodu tespiti ve DORUDAN EKLEME (generic tag yerine)
    postal_matches = re.findall(r'\b\d{5}\b', original_text)
    if postal_matches:
        # En byk posta kodunu al (oklu varsa en nemlisi genelde byk olandr)
        main_postal = max(postal_matches)
        features.append(f'POSTAL_{main_postal}')
    
    # Apartman tespiti
    if re.search(r'\b(apt|apartman|apart)\b', original_text, re.IGNORECASE):
        features.append('APARTMENT')
    
    # Kat bilgisi tespiti
    if re.search(r'\b(\d+\.?\s*(kat|kati)|kat\s*\d+|(zemin|bodrum|cati)\s*kat)\b', original_text, re.IGNORECASE):
        features.append('FLOOR_INFO')
    
    # Daire/kap numaras tespiti
    if re.search(r'\b(daire|d\.)\s*\d+\b', original_text, re.IGNORECASE):
        features.append('UNIT_NUMBER')
    
    # Site/kompleks tespiti
    if re.search(r'\b(site|sitesi|kompleks|kompleksi|rezidans|rezidansi|konut)\b', original_text, re.IGNORECASE):
        features.append('COMPLEX')
    
    # Blok bilgisi tespiti
    if re.search(r'\b(blok|bl\.?)\s*[a-zA-Z0-9]\b', original_text, re.IGNORECASE):
        features.append('BLOCK_INFO')
    
    # --- PHASE 9: FINAL CLEANUP ---
    # zel karakterleri ve noktalamay temizle (BERT iin)
    text = re.sub(r'[^\w\s]', ' ', text)
    
    # Fazla boluklar temizle
    text = re.sub(r'\s+', ' ', text).strip()
    
    # AKILLI KELME FLTRELEME: Anlaml tek harfleri koru!
    words = text.split()
    filtered_words = []
    for i, word in enumerate(words):
        # Saylar her zaman koru
        if word.isdigit():
            filtered_words.append(word)
        # Tek harf ama anlaml ise koru (A blok, B kaps vb.)
        elif len(word) == 1 and word.isalpha():
            # nceki veya sonraki kelimeye bak
            context_words = []
            if i > 0:
                context_words.append(words[i-1].lower())
            if i < len(words) - 1:
                context_words.append(words[i+1].lower())
            
            # Blok, kapi, daire vb. balamnda tek harf anlamldr
            meaningful_contexts = ['blok', 'kapi', 'kapisi', 'daire', 'apartmani', 'sitesi', 'mahallesi']
            if any(ctx in meaningful_contexts for ctx in context_words):
                filtered_words.append(word)
            # Yoksa ok ksa kelimeyi atla
        # Normal kelimeler (2+ karakter)
        elif len(word) >= 2:
            filtered_words.append(word)
    
    text = ' '.join(filtered_words)
    
    # --- PHASE 10: FEATURE INTEGRATION ---
    # Feature'lar metne entegre et (BERT iin ek sinyal)
    if features:
        feature_string = ' '.join(features)
        text = f"{text} {feature_string}"
    
    # Final temizlik
    text = re.sub(r'\s+', ' ', text).strip()
    
    return text

# --- 7. Dataset ---
class AddressDataset(torch.utils.data.Dataset):
    def __init__(self, encodings, labels):
        self.encodings = encodings
        self.labels = labels

    def __getitem__(self, idx):
        item = {key: torch.tensor(val[idx]) for key, val in self.encodings.items()}
        item['labels'] = torch.tensor(self.labels[idx])
        return item

    def __len__(self):
        return len(self.labels)

train_dataset = AddressDataset(train_encodings, y_train)
val_dataset = AddressDataset(val_encodings, y_val)

from sklearn.metrics import f1_score
import numpy as np
from transformers import TrainerCallback

# Training callback - basit LR tracking
class TrainingStepCallback(TrainerCallback):
    def __init__(self):
        self.logged_steps = set()
    
    def on_log(self, args, state, control, logs=None, **kwargs):
        if logs and 'learning_rate' in logs:
            step = state.global_step
            if step not in self.logged_steps:
                print(f" Step {step}: LR = {logs['learning_rate']:.2e}")
                self.logged_steps.add(step)

# Metrics hesaplama fonksiyonu
def compute_metrics(eval_pred):
    predictions, labels = eval_pred
    
    # Eer predictions tuple ise, ilk elemann al (preprocess_logits_for_metrics'ten gelirse)
    if isinstance(predictions, tuple):
        predictions = predictions[0]
    
    # Tensor'lar numpy'a evir
    if isinstance(predictions, torch.Tensor):
        predictions = predictions.cpu().numpy()
    if isinstance(labels, torch.Tensor):
        labels = labels.cpu().numpy()
    
    # Eer predictions 2D ise (batch_size, 1) flatten et
    if len(predictions.shape) > 1:
        predictions = predictions.flatten()
    if len(labels.shape) > 1:
        labels = labels.flatten()
    
    # F1 Score hesapla (predictions zaten argmax'lanm)
    f1 = f1_score(labels, predictions, average='macro')
    
    return {'f1': f1}

# GPU OOM nleme - Logits preprocessing
def preprocess_logits_for_metrics(logits, labels):
    """Logits'i argmax'layarak memory kullanmn azaltr"""
    pred_ids = torch.argmax(logits, dim=-1)
    return pred_ids, labels

model.to("cuda")

# --- 8. Fine-tuning Parametreleri ---
training_args = TrainingArguments(
    output_dir='./results_imbalance_baseline',  # Baseline model iin ayr klasr
    num_train_epochs=16,
    per_device_train_batch_size=96,
    per_device_eval_batch_size=96,
    learning_rate=4e-4,
    warmup_steps=10000,
    weight_decay=0.01,
    lr_scheduler_type="cosine",
    eval_strategy="steps",
    eval_steps=1000,
    save_strategy="steps", 
    save_steps=1000,
    load_best_model_at_end=True,
    save_total_limit=3,
    metric_for_best_model="f1",
    greater_is_better=True,
    report_to=[],
    logging_steps=1000,
    #eval_delay=10000,
    max_grad_norm= 1.0,  # Gradient clipping
    fp16=True
)

# Trainer
trainer = Trainer(
    model=model,
    args=training_args,
    train_dataset=train_dataset,
    eval_dataset=val_dataset,
    compute_metrics=compute_metrics,
    callbacks=[TrainingStepCallback()],
    preprocess_logits_for_metrics=preprocess_logits_for_metrics
)

print(" Baseline Trainer hazr! (Class weights yok - baseline iin)")

from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, confusion_matrix, accuracy_score, precision_recall_fscore_support
import numpy as np

# Validation seti iin tahmin yap
print("Validation seti iin tahminler yaplyor...")

# NEML: Predictions' hzl ve verimli ekilde ek
try:
    # nce normal trainer.predict() dene
    predictions = trainer.predict(val_dataset)
    print(f" trainer.predict() baarl! Type: {type(predictions)}")
    
    # Predictions' doru ekilde al
    if hasattr(predictions, 'predictions'):
        logits = predictions.predictions
        print(" predictions.predictions kullanld")
    elif isinstance(predictions, tuple) and len(predictions) > 0:
        logits = predictions[0]  # Tuple ise ilk eleman al
        print(f" predictions[0] kullanld, tuple length: {len(predictions)}")
    else:
        logits = predictions
        print(" predictions direkt kullanld")
    
    # Numpy array'e evir
    if hasattr(logits, 'cpu'):
        logits = logits.cpu().numpy()
    elif hasattr(logits, 'numpy'):
        logits = logits.numpy()
    
    print(f" Logits shape: {logits.shape}")
    
except Exception as e:
    print(f" trainer.predict() hatas: {e}")
    print(" Optimize edilmi manuel prediction balyor...")
    
    # OPTIMIZE EDLM MANUEL PREDCTON - BATCH PROCESSING
    from torch.utils.data import DataLoader
    
    # DataLoader ile batch processing
    val_dataloader = DataLoader(val_dataset, batch_size=128, shuffle=False)  # Byk batch size
    
    model.eval()
    all_logits = []
    
    print(f" Toplam batch says: {len(val_dataloader)}")
    
    with torch.no_grad():
        for i, batch in enumerate(val_dataloader):
            # Batch'i GPU'ya gnder
            inputs = {k: v.to(model.device) for k, v in batch.items() if k != 'labels'}
            
            # Forward pass
            outputs = model(**inputs)
            batch_logits = outputs.logits.cpu()  # CPU'ya al
            all_logits.append(batch_logits)
            
            # Progress gster
            if (i + 1) % 10 == 0 or (i + 1) == len(val_dataloader):
                print(f"    Batch {i+1}/{len(val_dataloader)} tamamland")
    
    # Tm logits'leri birletir
    logits = torch.cat(all_logits, dim=0).numpy()
    print(f" Optimize manuel prediction tamamland! Shape: {logits.shape}")

print(f" Labels shape: {len(y_val)}")

# Logits'ten argmax al
y_pred = np.argmax(logits, axis=1)
y_true = np.array(y_val)

# Boyutlar kontrol et
print(f" y_pred shape: {y_pred.shape}")
print(f" y_true shape: {y_true.shape}")

# Eer boyutlar uyumsuzsa dzelt
if len(y_pred) != len(y_true):
    min_len = min(len(y_pred), len(y_true))
    y_pred = y_pred[:min_len]
    y_true = y_true[:min_len]
    print(f" Boyut uyumsuzluu dzeltildi. Yeni boyut: {len(y_pred)}")

# Temel metrikler
accuracy = accuracy_score(y_true, y_pred)
precision, recall, f1, support = precision_recall_fscore_support(y_true, y_pred, average='macro', zero_division=0)
precision_micro, recall_micro, f1_micro, _ = precision_recall_fscore_support(y_true, y_pred, average='micro', zero_division=0)
precision_weighted, recall_weighted, f1_weighted, _ = precision_recall_fscore_support(y_true, y_pred, average='weighted', zero_division=0)

print(f" GENEL PERFORMANCE METRKLER:")

print(f"    Micro Precision: {precision_micro:.4f}")

print(f"    Micro F1-Score: {f1_micro:.4f}")
print(f"    Weighted Precision: {precision_weighted:.4f}")
print(f"    Weighted Recall: {recall_weighted:.4f}")
print(f"    Weighted F1-Score: {f1_weighted:.4f}")

# Her label iin F1 skorunu yazdr (bykten ke srala)
print(f"\n Her Label in F1 Skoru (Bykten Ke):")
class_labels = label_encoder.inverse_transform(np.arange(num_labels))

# Sralama iin tuple listesi olutur
label_f1_support = list(zip(class_labels, f1_per_class, support_per_class))
label_f1_support_sorted = sorted(label_f1_support, key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)
for label, f1_score_val, support_val in label_f1_support_sorted:
    print(f"   Label: {label} | F1: {f1_score_val:.4f} | Support: {support_val}")

# Confusion Matrix analizi
print(f"\n CONFUSION MATRIX ANALZ:")
cm = confusion_matrix(y_true, y_pred)

# Toplam TP, TN, FP, FN hesapla (multi-class iin)
total_tp = np.sum(np.diag(cm))  # Doru tahminler
total_samples = np.sum(cm)
total_fn_fp = total_samples - total_tp  # Yanl tahminler

print(f"    Toplam Doru Tahmin (TP): {total_tp:,}")
print(f"    Toplam Yanl Tahmin (FP+FN): {total_fn_fp:,}")
print(f"    Toplam Sample: {total_samples:,}")
print(f"    Accuracy: {total_tp/total_samples:.4f}")

# Class-wise detayl analiz

print(f"    Toplam snf says: {len(np.unique(y_true))}")

# En iyi ve en kt performans gsteren snflar bul
precision_per_class, recall_per_class, f1_per_class, support_per_class = precision_recall_fscore_support(y_true, y_pred, average=None, zero_division=0)

# NaN deerleri 0 ile deitir (hi rnei olmayan snflar iin)
precision_per_class = np.nan_to_num(precision_per_class)
recall_per_class = np.nan_to_num(recall_per_class)
f1_per_class = np.nan_to_num(f1_per_class)

if len(precision_per_class) > 0:
    best_precision_idx = np.argmax(precision_per_class)
    worst_precision_idx = np.argmin(precision_per_class)
    best_recall_idx = np.argmax(recall_per_class)
    worst_recall_idx = np.argmin(recall_per_class)
    best_f1_idx = np.argmax(f1_per_class)
    worst_f1_idx = np.argmin(f1_per_class)
    
    print(f"    En iyi Precision: Class {best_precision_idx} = {precision_per_class[best_precision_idx]:.4f}")
    print(f"    En kt Precision: Class {worst_precision_idx} = {precision_per_class[worst_precision_idx]:.4f}")
    print(f"    En iyi Recall: Class {best_recall_idx} = {recall_per_class[best_recall_idx]:.4f}")
    print(f"    En kt Recall: Class {worst_recall_idx} = {recall_per_class[worst_recall_idx]:.4f}")
    print(f"    En iyi F1: Class {best_f1_idx} = {f1_per_class[best_f1_idx]:.4f}")
    print(f"    En kt F1: Class {worst_f1_idx} = {f1_per_class[worst_f1_idx]:.4f}")

# Support dalm
print(f"\n SUPPORT DAILIMI:")
if len(support_per_class) > 0:
    print(f"    En fazla rnei olan snf: {np.max(support_per_class)} rnek")
    print(f"    En az rnei olan snf: {np.min(support_per_class)} rnek")
    print(f"    Ortalama rnek says: {np.mean(support_per_class):.1f}")
    if np.min(support_per_class) > 0:
        print(f"    Support imbalance ratio: {np.max(support_per_class)/np.min(support_per_class):.1f}")

# Class imbalance etkisi
print(f"\n CLASS IMBALANCE ETKS:")
if len(y_true) > 0:
    class_distribution = np.bincount(y_true) / len(y_true)
    print(f"    En byk snf oran: {np.max(class_distribution):.4f}")
    print(f"    En kk snf oran: {np.min(class_distribution):.4f}")

# --- 11. Eitim Sonularnn Grselletirilmesi ---
print("\n--- BASELINE MODEL ETM GRAFKLER ZLYOR ---")

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

try:
    # Training history'den verileri ek
    history = trainer.state.log_history
    
    # Training ve validation verilerini ayr
    train_logs = [log for log in history if 'loss' in log and 'eval_loss' not in log]
    eval_logs = [log for log in history if 'eval_loss' in log]
    
    # Veri ereveleri olutur
    train_df = pd.DataFrame(train_logs)
    eval_df = pd.DataFrame(eval_logs)
    
    # 2x2 subplot olutur
    fig, (ax1, ax2, ax3) = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(18, 6))
    fig.suptitle('BERT Fine-tuning Eitim Sonular (BASELINE - Top500+Bottom500)', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold')
    
    # 1. Training vs Validation Loss (Ayn grafikte)
    if not train_df.empty and 'loss' in train_df.columns:
        ax1.plot(train_df['step'], train_df['loss'], 'b-', linewidth=2, label='Training Loss')
    if not eval_df.empty and 'eval_loss' in eval_df.columns:
        ax1.plot(eval_df['step'], eval_df['eval_loss'], 'r-', linewidth=2, label='Validation Loss')
    
    ax1.set_title('Training vs Validation Loss (Baseline)', fontweight='bold')
    ax1.set_xlabel('Step')
    ax1.set_ylabel('Loss')
    ax1.grid(True, alpha=0.3)
    ax1.legend()
    
    # 2. F1 Score
    if not eval_df.empty and 'eval_f1' in eval_df.columns:
        ax2.plot(eval_df['step'], eval_df['eval_f1'], 'g-', linewidth=2, label='F1 Score')
        ax2.set_title('F1 Score (Validation) - Baseline', fontweight='bold')
        ax2.set_xlabel('Step')
        ax2.set_ylabel('F1 Score')
        ax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3)
        ax2.legend()
        
        # En iyi F1 score'u gster
        best_f1 = eval_df['eval_f1'].max()
        best_step = eval_df.loc[eval_df['eval_f1'].idxmax(), 'step']
        ax2.axhline(y=best_f1, color='red', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)
        ax2.text(0.02, 0.95, f'En yi F1: {best_f1:.4f}\n(Step: {best_step})', 
                transform=ax2.transAxes, fontsize=10, verticalalignment='top',
                bbox=dict(boxstyle='round', facecolor='wheat', alpha=0.8))
    
    # 3. Learning Rate
    if not train_df.empty and 'learning_rate' in train_df.columns:
        ax3.plot(train_df['step'], train_df['learning_rate'], 'purple', linewidth=2, label='Learning Rate')
        ax3.set_title('Learning Rate Schedule', fontweight='bold')
        ax3.set_xlabel('Step')
        ax3.set_ylabel('Learning Rate')
        ax3.grid(True, alpha=0.3)
        ax3.legend()
        ax3.ticklabel_format(style='scientific', axis='y', scilimits=(0,0))
    
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.savefig('imbalance_baseline_results.png', dpi=300, bbox_inches='tight')
    plt.show()
    
    # zet istatistikler yazdr
    print("\n" + "="*60)
    print(" BASELINE MODEL ETM ZET")
    print("="*60)
    
    print(f" Dataset: Top 500 + Bottom 500 labels ({num_labels} snf)")
    print(f" Class Weight: BASELINE (weight yok)")
    
    if not train_df.empty:
        final_train_loss = train_df['loss'].iloc[-1]
        print(f" Son Training Loss: {final_train_loss:.4f}")
    
    if not eval_df.empty:
        final_val_loss = eval_df['eval_loss'].iloc[-1]
        best_f1 = eval_df['eval_f1'].max()
        final_f1 = eval_df['eval_f1'].iloc[-1]
        print(f" Son Validation Loss: {final_val_loss:.4f}")
        print(f" En yi F1 Score: {best_f1:.4f}")
        print(f" Son F1 Score: {final_f1:.4f}")
    
    if not train_df.empty and 'learning_rate' in train_df.columns:
        final_lr = train_df['learning_rate'].iloc[-1]
        initial_lr = train_df['learning_rate'].iloc[0]
        print(f" Balang Learning Rate: {initial_lr:.2e}")
        print(f" Son Learning Rate: {final_lr:.2e}")
        print(f" LR Azalma Oran: {(final_lr/initial_lr)*100:.1f}%")
    
    print("="*60)
    print(" Baseline grafik 'imbalance_baseline_results.png' olarak kaydedildi!")
    print(" Sonraki adm: Class weight ekleyerek karlatrma yapabilirsiniz!")
    
except Exception as e:
    print(f" Grafik oluturma hatas: {e}")
    print(" Training history verilerine eriilemedi.")
